    <h2>CarTakeBack</h2>

<h3>Car/motorcycle</h3>

<p>Scrapping your car or motorcycle with CarTakeBack will ensure you receive the DVLA Certificate of Destruction required to complete your application to receive the funding from TfL. Motorcycles will be collected free of charge and issue a Notification of Destruction as proof it has been recycled.</p>

<p><a href="https://www.cartakeback.com/tfl-ulez-scrappage-scheme">See CarTakeBack's car/motorcycle offer.</a></p>

<h3>Van</h3>

<p>Scrapping your van will ensure you receive the DVLA Certificate of Destruction required to complete your application to receive the funding from TfL. Vans will be offered free collection from any address.</p>

<p><a href="https://www.cartakeback.com/TfL-Van-Scrappage-Scheme">See CarTakeBack's van offer.</a></p> 
</div>
 <div class="clearfix">
    <div class="image-box campaign-graphic right-float">
    
