    <h2>EMR (European Metal Recycling)</h2>

<p>EMR can recycle your van at five Authorised Treatment Facilities (ATF's) located across London: Brentford, Canning Town, Wandsworth, Mitcham and Willesden. EMR can also arrange collections on request. As a fully licensed ATF EMR scrap your van in an environmentally friendly way and contact DVLA to deregister your vehicle whilst paying you a fair price for your end of life van.</p>

<p><a href="http://www.vehiclescrappage.com/">See EMR's van offer.</a></p> 
</div>
 
